item.title: How do i make a rsps?
item.dc:creator: @sp11k3t3ht3rd sp11k3t3ht3rd
item.description:
@sp11k3t3ht3rd wrote:

[quote=“noobs are ftw, post:5, topic:341073”][quote author=kingman002 link=topic=437466.msg3214933#msg3214933 date=1274590369]
For one, go to the download section and download a source and client, my suggestion, a delta source, easy to code and compatible with a lot of client

u need no-ip so go to no-ip.com and sign up, create a domain and make ur ip, so like runescape.no-ip.biz

install no-ip

then you need to port forward so thats a whole new guide, which there is millions out

then after u portforward, open up no-ip duc then ur server, and other ppl can get on
[/quote]

y get more people into 317 r u an idiot everything has been done to them so they all the same dl a 508+[/quote]

This is just my opinion, but I personally thing 317 are the best. I hate 508+.
